snippet.title: Battlefront III Internal Trailer v6.
snippet.description:
Hi!

This is an older version of the internal trailer that was leaked for BF3. It shows a lot of unseen footage and is a really good indication of what the game was gonna turn out to be. 

Please, before you complain about the watermark, just ask yourself why I would put this file through and editor in order to make a new, clean copy?

*If any Free Radical/LucasArts/DICE/EA developer would like to get in touch with me to discuss details about this cancelled project, please do! I love hearing more about the game :)
